<view class="page">
  <view class="hero-card">
    <view class="hero-title">撮合流程</view>
    <view class="hero-text">平台先做信息服务和线下商务对接，帮助双方更快确认是否值得深入沟通。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-title">流程步骤</view>
  <view class="timeline">
    <view class="step card" wx:for="{{steps}}" wx:key="title">
      <view class="step-index">{{item.displayIndex}}</view>
      <view class="step-body">
        <view class="step-title">{{item.title}}</view>
        <view class="step-text">{{item.text}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-title">平台边界</view>
  <view class="card notice">
    <view class="notice-title">平台边界</view>
    <view class="notice-text">当前阶段不提供线上交易、支付结算或算力调度，重点提供信息发布、意向登记、企业认证和线下商务撮合。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="button-primary" bindtap="goMatch">申请人工撮合</view>
</view>
